_:N8f1c925a6e9b47c88bc583cd56ffb196 <http://schema.org/description> "The Boundary Commission for Wales (BCW) carries out boundary reviews of parliamentary constituencies in Wales, and submits its recommendations to the government. BCW is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government ." .
